This paper is about a new algorithm for contextual bandits, which is a problem in machine learning and decision making. The paper proposes a parameter-free and efficient algorithm that is optimal in terms of dynamic regret. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), and computational engineering (cs.CE).
